Mark Down Calendar Web Service
The below webservices are exposed as a part of this app.

mdc-service-controller : Mdc Service Controller

GET /mdcService/fetchMarchdownCalendar

Response Class (Status 200)

Response Content Type (application/json)

Response Messages
HTTP Status Code	Reason	Response Model	Headers
401                 Unauthorized
403                 Forbidden
404                 Not Found

Curl
************

Request Headers
{
  "Accept": "application/json"
}
